291
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,079
Due to his previous severe trauma,

292
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:08,920
Siyuan created an illusion

293
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,799
of his secondary personality,
Liao Zhibai,

294
