Siyuan.

572
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,639
I refused to believe it either,

573
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,320
but I've seen his drug test report.

574
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,920
His urine test result
came back positive.

575
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,079
You already knew?

576
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,159
Why didn't you tell me then?

577
00:37:27,079 --> 00:37:28,519
What's the point of telling you?

578
00:37:31,559 --> 00:37:33,280
Why should I let you suffer

579
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:36,360
what I've already suffered?

580
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:46,760
He's no longer around,

581
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,159
but you're still alive.

582
00:37:53,159 --> 00:37:54,280
So I thought

583
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,639
it would be good

584
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,960
if you had a good impression of him

585
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:04,880
in your memory.

586
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:14,559
What about you?

587
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:15,519
Me?

588
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,519
I'm already used to it.

589
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:21,639
I thought of many possibilities.

590
00:38:22,079 --> 00:38:23,159
Why would he do that?

591
00:38:25,039 --> 00:38:26,159
Was it because

592
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,159
he was undercover
and wanted to protect himself

593
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:31,400
or because he was forced to do so

594
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:33,700
and was unable to prove himself?

595
00:38:35,159 --> 00:38:36,119
Or

596
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:39,360
he was indeed a scum?

597
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,800
But I believe

598
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,800
that one day the truth will come out.

599
00:38:59,639 --> 00:39:00,159
Xia.

600
00:39:01,519 --> 00:39:02,360
Let's go together.

601
00:39:04,599 --> 00:39:05,639
I found a clue.

602
00:39:12,639 --> 00:39:13,400
Tai Shu?

603
00:39:51,134 --> 00:39:52,930
(May 29th, Yong'an Village's Fire)

604
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:14,280
How could it be you who is behind this?

605
00:40:16,639 --> 00:40:18,920
I'm the one
who archived the autopsy reports.

606
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,159
If possible,

607
00:40:39,559 --> 00:40:40,920
it would be nice to see you again.

608
00:41:00,690 --> 00:41:04,540
(Qi's Pharmacy)

609
00:41:04,559 --> 00:41:06,639
Liao Siyuan, hurry up.

610
00:41:10,519 --> 00:41:11,159
Hurry up.

611
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:13,280
When Mom comes back after drinking

612
00:41:13,599 --> 00:41:14,559
and sees us,

613
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,639
neither of us can leave.

614
00:41:18,079 --> 00:41:18,960
You two.

615
00:41:20,639 --> 00:41:21,159
We're doomed.

616
00:41:21,740 --> 00:41:23,800
What you fear most
always finds its way to you.

617
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,079
Go back first. Let's go.

618
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:27,639
You two!

619
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,440
I'm talking to you two.

620
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:34,519
Where are you going?

621
00:41:37,519 --> 00:41:39,519
Our school's organizing

622
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:40,840
a camping trip.

623
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,840
We have to go three...

624
00:41:43,860 --> 00:41:45,300
Five days and three nights.

625
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:46,860
Xia happens to be on her annual leave,

626
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,040
so I'm taking her with me.

627
00:41:48,080 --> 00:41:49,070
She can drive.

628
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,079
Camping?

629
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:54,079
I haven't gone to one for a long time.

630
00:41:54,580 --> 00:41:55,550
I want to join you too.

631
00:41:55,639 --> 00:41:56,679
I'll pack my bags now.

632
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:57,679
Mom.

633
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:00,159
The ones going are all young people.

634
00:42:00,239 --> 00:42:01,400
Young people?

635
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,280
Do you think I'm old?

636
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,119
No.

637
00:42:05,140 --> 00:42:06,040
Their school has a rule

638
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:07,940
that says family members
aren't allowed to join.

639
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:08,720
They're all kids.

640
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:10,300
What's the point of playing with them?

641
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,440
We don't drink either.

642
00:42:12,559 --> 00:42:15,760
What school doesn't allow drinking
and doesn't allow parents to join?

643
00:42:16,420 --> 00:42:17,800
It will close down sooner or later.

644
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,360
Li Zhi.

645
00:42:20,880 --> 00:42:21,519
Hurry.

646
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:23,150
What's the matter, Ms. Meihua?

647
00:42:24,159 --> 00:42:25,280
This is Li Zhi.

648
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:26,880
My son, Liao Siyuan.

649
00:42:27,039 --> 00:42:28,519
My daughter, Qi Xia.

650
00:42:29,159 --> 00:42:30,440
My good friend, Li Zhi,

651
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,740
is from the same school as you.

652
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:34,060
Thanks to her for blocking the drinks
for me last night.

653
00:42:34,079 --> 00:42:36,880
Otherwise, those persons
would have gotten me drunk.

654
00:42:38,639 --> 00:42:40,000
Good friend?

655
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:42,280
Hello, Aunt Li Zhi.

656
00:42:43,559 --> 00:42:44,719
Darn you!

657
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:46,039
Hey!

658
00:42:46,039 --> 00:42:47,159
We know each other.

659
00:42:48,020 --> 00:42:48,920
We're classmates.

660
00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:49,760
We know each other.

661
00:42:50,239 --> 00:42:51,639
Yes, you're from the same school.

662
00:42:51,639 --> 00:42:52,800
Aren't you going camping?

663
00:42:53,159 --> 00:42:54,000
Are you not going?

664
00:42:54,639 --> 00:42:55,480
Yes, camping.

665
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:56,159
I'm going.

666
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:58,360
My car happened to run out of gas.

667
00:42:58,400 --> 00:42:59,519
I'll carpool with you later.

668
00:42:59,599 --> 00:43:00,760
Sure, no problem.

669
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:03,000
You just filled up your car with gas.

670
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:09,800
How come they're together?

671
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:10,880
How would I know?

672
00:43:12,159 --> 00:43:13,559
I knew it.

673
00:43:15,159 --> 00:43:15,840
Alright.

674
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:17,159
Good luck.

675
00:43:19,159 --> 00:43:19,920
It's late.

676
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:20,639
Hurry and pack up.

677
00:43:20,639 --> 00:43:21,549
Or we'll be late.

678
00:43:21,550 --> 00:43:22,790
- I haven't taken my bag.
- Go.

679
00:43:22,790 --> 00:43:23,640
I'll go help him.

680
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:24,920
Xia.

681
00:43:31,119 --> 00:43:31,760
Mom.

682
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:38,800
You two think you're all grown up now.

683
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:40,580
Each one is more stubborn than the last.

684
00:43:40,580 --> 00:43:42,040
If it hadn't run into you head-on,

685
00:43:42,060 --> 00:43:43,580
you would have been somewhere now.

686
00:43:46,199 --> 00:43:47,159
Tell me the truth.

687
00:43:47,580 --> 00:43:48,880
Where on earth are you going?

688
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:52,599
We're just going out for a few days.

689
00:43:53,639 --> 00:43:54,559
I don't believe you.

690
00:43:54,559 --> 00:43:55,639
It's true.

691
00:43:57,960 --> 00:43:58,639
Alright.

692
00:43:59,780 --> 00:44:01,440
All that matters is that you're happy.

693
00:44:02,960 --> 00:44:03,639
We're going.

694
00:44:08,519 --> 00:44:09,519
Alright, we're going.

695
00:44:09,519 --> 00:44:10,079
Okay.

696
00:44:10,199 --> 00:44:11,320
Don't drink so much.

697
00:44:12,039 --> 00:44:12,920
You're so fussy.

698
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:15,080
I'll have fun with you again
when I'm back.

699
00:44:15,080 --> 00:44:15,660
Sure.

700
00:44:15,880 --> 00:44:17,000
Drive safe.

701
00:44:18,040 --> 00:44:19,620
Take good care of your brother.

702
00:44:19,639 --> 00:44:20,760
Don't worry!

703
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:23,639
Have fun!

704
00:44:52,195 --> 00:44:56,633
♪The night stretches long,
like an endless hallway♪

705
00:44:57,995 --> 00:45:03,152
♪Without moonlight
or a god to guide the way♪

706
00:45:03,789 --> 00:45:08,660
♪Memories drip
within the center of my heart♪

707
00:45:08,915 --> 00:45:13,679
♪Burning you away,
leaving only emptiness♪

708
00:45:13,886 --> 00:45:16,698
♪The distorted truth♪

709
00:45:16,876 --> 00:45:22,461
♪Is tampered with,
buried, and forgotten♪

710
00:45:25,110 --> 00:45:31,024
♪Beyond the embers,
the wound remains warm♪

711
00:45:31,190 --> 00:45:35,975
♪It lights up again♪

712
00:45:36,704 --> 00:45:42,337
♪Whose hands♪

713
00:45:42,592 --> 00:45:45,916
♪Are pulling the strings?♪

714
00:45:46,073 --> 00:45:48,500
♪Who stands at the end of the lie?♪

715
00:45:48,509 --> 00:45:53,990
♪Behind the mask♪

716
00:45:54,343 --> 00:45:57,623
♪Whose softness♪

717
00:45:57,913 --> 00:45:59,735
♪Has decayed?♪

718
00:45:59,835 --> 00:46:03,543
♪Lift the dust, feel it with your soul♪

719
00:46:03,545 --> 00:46:08,470
♪The chains of destiny
have long bound us♪

720
00:46:08,715 --> 00:46:11,475
♪To each other♪

721
00:46:11,949 --> 00:46:14,414
♪If you don't die, I won't stop♪

722
00:46:14,482 --> 00:46:17,261
♪Let's witness together♪

723
00:46:17,365 --> 00:46:20,544
♪The end♪
